{
  "texts": [
    "For educators, JEEBench offers a valuable resource to gauge the potential of LLMs in enhancing education.",
    "By analyzing LLM performance on JEEBench tasks, lecturers can make informed decisions about integrating AI into their pedagogy, identifying areas where AI can supplement traditional teaching methods and areas where human intervention is crucial.",
    "The performance of JEEBench is assessed using various open-source and proprietary LLMs.",
    "Even the most proficient models in chemistry exhibit performance below random chance.",
    "For instance, the GPT-4 model in a zero-shot setting achieved an accuracy of 0.42, while the GPT-4 model with GPT-4+CoT+SelfCritique (SC) prompting attained 0.48 accuracy."
  ]
}